body_html: @poxvoculi: I have already asked the question on stack overflow, however, I haven't received any help. And I have also tried running the basic models (mnist and inception) and they seem to work fine. However, there is no documentation for actually creating a client program for any other algorithms, for instance, the models build using Tf.Learn API. Which is why I raised a concern here so that there could be some documentation for the same.
